# ── Screenshots / design docs ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Blanket-exclude loose screenshots/mockups in the repo root, but whitelist
# all images inside the website and arpg-game public directories — these
# are needed at runtime (marketing site, game loading screens, perk icons).
*.png
*.jpg
!artifacts/website/public/**/*.png
!artifacts/website/public/**/*.jpg
!artifacts/website/public/*.png
!artifacts/website/public/*.jpg
!artifacts/website/public/favicon.svg
!artifacts/arpg-game/public/grudges-logo.png
!artifacts/arpg-game/public/grudges-landing.png
!artifacts/arpg-game/public/grudges-loading-1.png
!artifacts/arpg-game/public/grudges-loading-2.png
!artifacts/arpg-game/public/bosslogo.png
!artifacts/arpg-game/public/icons/**/*.png

